I don't know about you guys, but
I'm starting to get a bit nervous.

rows.label: fev05_270_125_msg0003

Be careful not to say anything
disrespectful.

rows.label: fev05_270_125_msg0005

The audience chamber's just across
the courtyard. We'll be there in a jiffy.

rows.label: fev05_270_125_msg0006
rows.name: Well, we can hardly keep His Holiness waiting. Shall we head out?
